high_descs: Move to the right and face the counter with the green bin underneath.
Pick the spoon up from the counter.
Move to the left and turn to face the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the spoon up.
Go right and then right again to stand in front of the microwave cart.
Put the spoon down on the cart in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon down in front of a microwave.

high_descs: Move to the counter ahead of the fridge
Pick up a spoon from the counter
Move to the sink to the left of you
Clean the spoon in the sink
Move to the counter to the right of the fridge
Put the spoon on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon on the counter to the right of the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward to the right side of the counter by the recycling bin.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the side table containing the microwave.
Put the spoon on the table, in front of and to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon on a side table.
